		},
		{
			"uuid": "06596bd5-cd59-47f8-ade3-9075b1847e37",
			"title": "Inertia?",
			"description": "Maybe a slight inertia system could be interesting\nI decided to make it so speed ramps down really quickly when youre above a speed cap for sprinting or walking.  This doesnt feel floaty like ice, and also lets you feel like you can go fast...",
			"category": "14bc8dfc-382b-4779-a576-ff565ed63cbd",
			"steps": []
		},
		{
			"uuid": "072c2cc6-c3b5-4098-bea3-8598fa3f8d6b",
			"title": "COMMENT EVERYTHING",
			"description": "Need to add comments to all component functions since it can be confusing reading them not all under one big script.",
			"category": "14bc8dfc-382b-4779-a576-ff565ed63cbd",
			"steps": []
		},
		{
			"uuid": "0dec7a52-dcab-406a-9af0-80f80dec30bf",
			"title": "Add SFX for wall kicking",
			"description": "can probably be done similarily to the footstep component, just need to check the group of the remembered wall and apply a sfx for it",
			"category": "14bc8dfc-382b-4779-a576-ff565ed63cbd",
			"steps": []
		},
		{
			"uuid": "7ada93f1-5714-4961-9d8e-41acfc1014c5",
			"title": "Crouching Midair bug",
			"description": "When you crouch mid jump since I remember foot position of the player and move to that in a crouch it can be awkward and kinda hover you.  We might want to turn this into a feature where you can slam down (like ultrakill)",
